 Singer Wizkid has celebrated the birthday of his first son Boluwatife calling his first love as he clocks 10yrs old today full of excitement. Boluwatife celebrating his 10th birthday today said he has officially become a big boy and his father Wizkid celebrating him also confirmed his son has become a big boy and very surprised that his first love is already 10. Wizkid shared a photo with his son Boluwatife expressing his love for him, saying he loves him to the moon and back to show that his love for him is endless just as going to the moon and coming back. 